@@$TJvThreadTimer
<TITLE TJvThreadTimer overview>
<GROUP JVCL.AlarmsAndTimers.Timers>
  The TJvThreadTimer component is a replacement for the TTimer component, with a better accuracy 
  (1 millisecond). TJvThreadTimer uses a TJvThreadTimerclass thread instead of the Windows API timer 
  functions, and can have an accuracy of a millisecond, but it will consume more CPU than a TTimer.
